{"tid":332550,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"【第8回延長!】連登筆友計劃 (捌)","createTime":"2017-07-23T05:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T14:57:55.000Z","uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2067880d8c349f0cc368525b49e33924af1d188","tid":332550,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"今日電腦開極都load唔到呀屌！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">決定開埋今日俾巴絲join</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n延遲至今晚或聽日配對, 敬請原諒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yur3nhsv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyur3nhsv&h=7bf64041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表前記得睇左呢度先!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 每人獲配一巴一絲 + Greeting Question 既email 一封;</span></strong><br />\n而同時Admin會將你地分配俾其他巴絲打, 所以會有其他人主動Approach既情況出現, 各位唔需要大驚少怪  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>例: 假設A係其一參加人，佢會收到B、C嘅資料做佢嘅筆友（一巴一絲），而A嘅資料亦都會send去D到做另一個配對。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 每個email只可以交表 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1</span> 次</strong><br />\n(筆友唔啱你可以email我, 會再配俾你, 唔洗玩分身, 見者即block)<br />\n<br />\n第8回表格:<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/W9cMNZnerelMUTcr2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FW9cMNZnerelMUTcr2&d=T8Rla5ECJQFl2tgwsLfgl26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a25c881b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/W9cMNZnerelMUTcr2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">截Form時間:<br />\n7 月 23 日 (日), 晚上 11時正</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/IlyBnXu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt